data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Infection with Chronic hepatitis C genotype 1confirmed at screening;
* Anti-HCV positive；
* HCV RNA ≥1 × 10000IU / mL;
* Not treated with interferon and / or any other direct-acting antiviral (DAA) drug;
* Non-cirrhotic;
* Voluntarily sign informed consent.

Exclusion Criteria

Inclusion Criteria:

* Males or females, of any race, between 18 and 50 years of age, inclusive, at Screening;
* Body mass index between 18.0 and 28.0 kg/m2, inclusive, at Screening;
* Females of childbearing potential and male subjects will agree to use contraception from screening to the 6 months
